race.comment: SKEDADDLE LOUISE (1) turned in a solid run last start over 520m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (30.04). Better than last start and worth following up. ZIPPING ZODIAC (6) turned in a better effort at Wentworth Park last start, finishing second behind Zipping Dekkers (29.71) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Can feature again. MAX SHIRAZ (8) comes here off a placing in slick time (29.88) over 520m at this track. In form and looks a leading player again. GINNY'S RUN (2) won with authority last start. Big chance on that form.
